KENDRA SELLS

Kendra Sells is an Austin-native and lead singer of neo-soul band BluMoon. Kendra has been a huge part of building the San Marcos music scene, and has been a huge leader in making it more inclusive for non-rock based genres. She is truly one of a kind and is well-known for her mesmerizing  performances. BluMoon is releasing their sophomore album early 2019. Watch their local live performance below:
